text: "At the end of the day there is a lot of complications," Munn said. "I don't think either side of the road is clean, but I do think it's not OK when you try to stand on someone's shoulders and then throw dirt in their face, which is what I think they did with him."
title: Olivia Munn says Aaron Rodgers was estranged from family before they started dating

meta_data.description: The actress finally shed some light on her ex-boyfriend's strained relationship with his family.
